title: Guitar Legends For Heroes - 2017-11-29 - New York
description: This upload is dedicated to ALL those people fighting for OUR freedom, remember them, honour them >>> and please help all veterans who are still suffering!!! Please enjoy the music, share with friends (for FREE!!!) and please seed :) I use fast servers but also need your help, there's too much downloaders to handle. Stuff like this needs to be preserved for future generations of music lovers. Thanks to all the peers from everywhere seeding my huge archive, i love you! ================================================================================ AMERICA SALUTES YOU AND WALL STREET ROCKS PRESENTS: GUITAR LEGENDS FOR HEROES Terminal 5 - New York City, NY Taped: 11/29/17 - AXS.TV Airdate: 12/23/17 NTSC PRO DVD - Editing & Authoring: acady - Menu & Chapters Included Lineage: Satellite > DISH DVR 625 > S-Video Line In > Magnavox ZC320MW8B DVD Recorder > DVD+RW (XP Mode) > PC > TMPGEnc Authoring Works 5 (editing and authoring with Smart Rendering) > DVD A concert honoring those who serve in the military, veterans and their families.
